To delete FamilySync user data, please delete your user account through the in app settings menu. If your user data is not saved to an online account, merely uninstall the app. Please note that, if you join a family and are not the administrator, your data will persist through the family account even if you leave, or are removed from, the family. A family administrator can schedule the family data for deletion through the in app settings menu. Please email primitiveedgellc@gmail.com with any questions or concerns.
